{"tid":190834,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無試過同老細鬥屌？","createTime":"2017-04-07T11:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T02:38:34.000Z","uid":21402,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce20a08fa14b13bf2f43f43e8722ad26d16aa33e","tid":190834,"uid":21402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"我老細六十幾歲<br />\n係果d做野唔hea得要chur到準時食飯準時收工嘅人黎<br />\n今日我食完飯去左公園坐 果陣仲係lunch hour<br />\n跟住佢打過黎問我點解唔返公司坐 <br />\n之後我話而家仲係lunch hour 差唔多夠鐘我會返上黎<br />\n跟住佢就同我講：得喇，一陣你返黎執埋d野走<br />\n我返到公司就見到佢<br />\n即刻同佢講我屌你老母呀！<br />\n之後就同佢鬥屌<br />\n全層都聽到<br />\n屌完最後都係執野走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係好撚爽 咁大個仔第一屌老細屌足佢十八代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8976db04166fa9a78297b26bd37d1c9c6bdcfa03","tid":190834,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:30:16.000Z","msg":"係真的話<br />\n<br />\n比個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你<br />\n<br />\n呢d垃圾廢老 屌佢=塞車落佢個袋"},{"pid":"8c64d42b24bd313b274a24131efbc7400b45de9b","tid":190834,"uid":19431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n準備好搵工未？"},{"pid":"a5573f2ab30a7023720de8794f50342a1dde1924","tid":190834,"uid":8497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:31:43.000Z","msg":"雖然你老細係ON9<br />\n但下次見工個時諗定點解釋"},{"pid":"91590679949fe2cb93bde9ea26257af423850eb6","tid":190834,"uid":21402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:34:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係真的話<br />\n<br />\n比個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你<br />\n<br />\n呢d垃圾廢老 屌佢=塞車落佢個袋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji